03:10.116 --> 03:11.752
Pretty enough to buy a TV?

03:11.752 --> 03:12.885
Mhm.

03:12.885 --> 03:16.556
Yes! Roofie!

03:16.556 --> 03:18.625
Oh, you're the best friend a guy ever had.

03:18.625 --> 03:21.795
