04:47.146 --> 04:48.615
Sorry! Sorry!

04:48.615 --> 04:49.682
I dropped a bunch of these

04:49.682 --> 04:51.218
wobbly metal lunch trays.

04:51.218 --> 04:53.019
Sounded a lot like
thunder, though, didn't it?

04:54.821 --> 04:56.822
We would be willing to pay a lot of money

04:56.822 --> 04:59.158
to make this go away before, say,

04:59.158 --> 05:02.728
the parents' association were to find out?

05:02.728 --> 05:03.529
Gotcha.

05:03.529 --> 05:04.630
Ah!

05:04.630 --> 05:06.165
Here's Ms. Fatale now.

05:06.165 --> 05:08.535
Principal Herring, you wanted to see me?

05:08.535 --> 05:09.903
Hello.

05:09.903 --> 05:12.773
Ms. Fatale, this is Mr. Pacalioglu.

05:12.773 --> 05:14.141
