05:36.163 --> 05:38.130
Um, music!

05:38.130 --> 05:41.634
Music, uh, do you like music?

05:41.634 --> 05:43.637
I mean, I like music a lot.

05:43.637 --> 05:45.572
Y.

05:45.572 --> 05:46.505
Why do I like music?

05:46.505 --> 05:48.542
No! Y as in yes!

05:48.542 --> 05:50.776
Yeah, my dad was a saxophone player...

05:50.776 --> 05:52.745
Why is there no yes shortcut on this board?

05:52.745 --> 05:53.980
And he was really good unless

05:53.980 --> 05:54.980
