05:54.980 --> 05:56.649
Oh! Wait, there is a yes!

05:56.649 --> 05:58.752
I'm guessing you don't
want to hear about that.

05:58.752 --> 06:00.754
Oh, you do!

06:00.754 --> 06:02.189
- I do what?
- I don't know, Sue,

06:02.189 --> 06:03.956
I haven't talked about my father,

06:03.956 --> 06:06.158
not since...

06:06.158 --> 06:07.694
not since he hit the road.

06:07.694 --> 06:09.161
- Oh, shit.
- Boo!

06:09.161 --> 06:10.863
- Ahh!
- Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah,

06:10.863 --> 06:12.298
I'm mad at him too.

06:12.298 --> 06:14.000
Jesus.

06:14.000 --> 06:15.836
Millie, what are you doing here?

06:15.836 --> 06:17.838
Um, what are you doing here?

06:17.838 --> 06:20.106
I told Kevin I'd hang out
with his friend Roofie.

06:20.106 --> 06:21.173
Why? He can't even hear you!

06:21.173 --> 06:22.242
I know, but...

06:22.242 --> 06:23.776
Look, he doesn't need you!

06:23.776 --> 06:25.112
He's having a great time by himself.

06:25.112 --> 06:26.480
The year?

06:26.480 --> 06:28.247
1994.

06:28.247 --> 06:29.850
It was a cold winter,

06:29.850 --> 06:31.785
the kind of winter you felt in your bones.

06:31.785 --> 06:33.185
God, I miss my body.

06:33.185 --> 06:33.786
Yeah...

06:34.987 --> 06:37.090
Hey, I have an idea.

06:37.090 --> 06:38.824
Come with me!

06:38.824 --> 06:42.824
